data.description: No stairs! Main level condo with brand new flooring nestled in southeast Denver. Spacious 2bed 1bath with large closets and big living room. Bonus sun room too! Convenient location close to your dedicated covered carport space, and plenty of easy parking nearby for quick access. HOA includes an array of desirable amenities, including a pool, club house, tennis courts and many tree lined green belts throughout the community. HOA covers grounds maintenance, structure maintenance, sewer, snow removal, trash and water.  This would be an incredible home or investment property. Quick closing available.
